creator: Game and tools, Daniel Rico
descriptionHtml:
Play and learn the means of transport in English and Spanish, teach your children to concentrate and learn words in another language with super fun images for children to learn the means of transport, you can correctly hear pronounced names of vehicles in English and Spanish, You can also listen to the pronunciation more slowly if you wish for a correct learning, each image card has real sound of the means of transport, additionally it has a beautiful background melody so that your children learn happier.

1. Air transport such as helicopter, plane, jet, rocket, spaceship, plane.
2. Land or land vehicles such as cars, buses, trams, trains, excavators, fire trucks, ambulances, police vehicles, trucks, bicycles, excavators, caravans, taxis, coaches, limousines, trucks, motorcycles, trucks, tractors.
3. Water vehicles such as submarines, boats, boats, canoes, ferries, motor boats, sailboats

✔ vehicle sounds

✔ Photos of vehicles with HD quality
✔ Transportation spelling

✔ Transport cards
